		<title>Central Bank of Canada says a thing or two about Bitcoin</title>
		<link>http://kosmatos.com/2014/05/01/central-bank-of-canada-says-a-thing-or-two-on-bitcoin/</link>
		<comments>http://kosmatos.com/2014/05/01/central-bank-of-canada-says-a-thing-or-two-on-bitcoin/#respond</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2014 15:59:52 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Odi Kosmatos]]></dc:creator>
